<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-agreements.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61"><a href="rus-register-transactions-with-reference-to-agreements.html" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/rus-agreements.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61">Register transactions with reference to agreements</a></li>
